## 🍽️ RESTAURANT ORDER SYSTEM - ALL ORDER TYPES

### === 1. PICKUP/TAKEAWAY ORDERS (No reservation needed) ===

### Create pickup order
POST http://localhost:5005/api/orders/pickup
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "menuItemId": "64a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345a",
      "name": "Phở Bò Tái",
      "price": 85000,
      "quantity": 2,
      "customizations": "Ít hành",
      "notes": "Không cần rau thơm"
    },
    {
      "menuItemId": "64a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345b", 
      "name": "Chả cá Lã Vọng",
      "price": 120000,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ],
  "customerName": "Nguyen Van A",
  "phoneNumber": "0123456789",
  "scheduledTime": "2025-08-08T21:00:00Z",
  "pickupInstructions": "Gọi khi đến quầy",
  "specialInstructions": "Đóng gói cẩn thận"
}

### Get all pickup orders (for staff)
GET http://localhost:5005/api/orders/pickup?status=ready&date=2025-08-08

### Confirm pickup order (staff accepts order - pending → preparing)
PUT http://localhost:5005/api/orders/pickup/{{pickupOrderNumber}}/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "estimatedTime": 25
}

### Mark pickup order as ready (preparing → ready)
PUT http://localhost:5005/api/orders/pickup/{{pickupOrderNumber}}/ready

### Complete pickup (customer picked up)
PUT http://localhost:5005/api/orders/pickup/{{pickupOrderNumber}}/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pickedUpBy": "Nguyen Van A",
  "paymentMethod": "cash"
}

### === 2. DINE-IN ORDERS (Need reservation first) ===

### Get available tables
GET http://localhost:5006/api/tables?date=2025-08-08&time=20:00&partySize=4

### Step 1: Create reservation
POST http://localhost:5006/api/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tableId": "{{TABLE_ID}}",
  "reservationDate": "2025-08-08",
  "startTime": "20:00",
  "endTime": "22:00",
  "partySize": 4,
  "occasion": "birthday",
  "specialRequests": "Window seat preferred"
}

### Check reservation details before checkin
GET http://localhost:5006/api/reservations/{{reservationNumber}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Step 2: Check-in when arriving at restaurant
PUT http://localhost:5006/api/reservations/{{reservationNumber}}/checkin
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Step 3: Order food at table
POST http://localhost:5005/api/orders/dine-in
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reservationId": "{{reservationId}}",
  "reservationNumber": "{{reservationNumber}}",
  "items": [
    {
      "menuItemId": "64a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345c",
      "name": "Gỏi cuốn tôm thịt",
      "price": 45000,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "menuItemId": "64a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345d",
      "name": "Bún bò Huế",
      "price": 95000,
      "quantity": 4,
      "customizations": "Cay vừa"
    }
  ],
  "specialInstructions": "Phục vụ gỏi cuốn trước"
}

### Step 4: Kitchen updates order status
PUT http://localhost:5005/api/orders/dine-in/ORD-1723220123456-890/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "cooking",
  "note": "Started cooking at 19:15"
}

### Step 5: Mark order as served
PUT http://localhost:5005/api/orders/dine-in/ORD-1723220123456-890/serve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "servedBy": "Waiter John"
}

### Step 6: Get all orders for a reservation
GET http://localhost:5006/api/reservations/{{reservationNumber}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Step 7: Check-out when leaving restaurant
PUT http://localhost:5006/api/reservations/{{reservationNumber}}/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### === 3. DELIVERY ORDERS (Existing system) ===

### 🚚 DELIVERY ORDER - Correct Format
POST {{baseUrl}}:5005/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "menuItemId": "64a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345a",
      "quantity": 2,
      "specialInstructions": "Extra herbs please"
    },
    {
      "menuItemId": "64a1b2c3d4e5f6789012345b", 
      "quantity": 1,
      "specialInstructions": "Medium spicy"
    }
  ],
  "delivery": {
    "type": "delivery",
    "address": {
      "street": "123 Nguyen Trai",
      "district": "District 1", 
      "city": "Ho Chi Minh City",
      "phoneNumber": "0123456789"
    }
  },
  "payment": {
    "method": "cash"
  },
  "notes": "Call when arrived"
}

### === COMPARISON SUMMARY ===

# 🏃 PICKUP/TAKEAWAY:
# - No reservation needed
# - Customer calls ahead
# - Pay at pickup
# - Status: pending → preparing → ready → picked_up → completed

# 🍽️ DINE-IN:
# - Requires table reservation
# - Order at table after check-in
# - Service charge included
# - Status: ordered → cooking → served → dining → completed
# - Table management integration

# 🚚 DELIVERY:
# - No reservation needed  
# - Address required
# - Delivery fee included
# - Status: pending → confirmed → preparing → ready → out_for_delivery → delivered → completed
